7dfkwHAvYrzRQcIe%2F4zZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=ed983a72\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0GfzPr1IcvA</a><br />\n<br />\n呢次講吓點樣溫暖輕鬆提高別人對你的評價, 輕鬆獲取信任!<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=MwZzePErpMg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DMwZzePErpMg&d=tZkk7dfkwHAvYrzRQcIe%2F4zZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=75746679\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=MwZzePErpMg</a><br />\n<br />\n呢次講吓點樣用模仿輕鬆提高別人對你的好感,輕鬆獲取別人信任!<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PxalLMq_gqw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DPxalLMq_gqw&d=tZkk7dfkwHAvYrzRQcIe%2F4zZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=3a48c9c6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PxalLMq_gqw</a>"},{"pid":"5345d816231edf799e1f773de1fe0f81c9ada994","tid":982922,"uid":78029,"like":18,"dislike":2,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T13:37:53.000Z","msg":"呢次講吓教科書唔會教的香港歷史, 例如未開埠前有香港人幫英軍補給, 香港人唔係大中華史觀講到咁愛國 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3VyGBBak9Qs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D3VyGBBak9Qs&d=tZkk7dfkwHAvYrzRQcIe%2F4zZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=52f07b2e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3VyGBBak9Qs</a><br />\n<br />\n呢集講吓新學到的知識有幾快會被遺忘, 又會遺忘幾多, 同埋我地有咩方法去減少遺忘, 將學到的知識由短期記憶轉化成長期記憶<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gHNy4VD0nEA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DgHNy4VD0nEA&d=tZkk7dfkwHAvYrzRQcIe%2F4zZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=a204711d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gHNy4VD0nEA</a><br />\n<br />\n呢集講吓科學界點睇「世界上有無外星人? 如果有, 點解外星人無和我們接觸?」呢個問題<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3ob8lj7OM5Q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D3ob8lj7OM5Q&d=tZkk7dfkwHAvYrzRQcIe%2F4zZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=484fe2c9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3ob8lj7OM5Q</a><br />\n<br />\n呢集想講吓近年科學點睇「成年後腦袋係咪不再進步, 只會退化?」呢個問題, 從而介紹吓 我地可以點樣增加記憶力<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=21byiVTSZhI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D21byiVTSZhI&d=tZkk7dfkwHAvYrzRQcIe%2F4zZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=ac3ecaac\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=21byiVTSZhI</a><br />\n<br />\n呢集由大腦科學角度講吓靈魂出竅/離體經驗係咩一回事, 科學界有無方法重現靈魂出竅<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JhjpNvT-U4g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DJhjpNvT-U4g&d=tZkk7dfkwHAvYrzRQcIe%2F4zZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=798d1177\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JhjpNvT-U4g</a><br />\n<br />\n呢集由大腦科學角度講吓一D因為腦部受傷而成為奇才的人, 從而睇下未來科技有無可能將我地由普通人突然變成奇才<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=eCEv3hfdco8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DeCEv3hfdco8&d=tZkk7dfkwHAvYrzRQcIe%2F4zZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=40ef79e0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=eCEv3hfdco8</a><br />\n<br />\n第一集係由大腦科學, 心理學角度講吓愛情行為, 例如點解分手咁痛苦, 點解開始拍拖時會睇唔到對方缺點: <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mgTq1gYCsZA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DmgTq1gYCsZA&d=tZkk7dfkwHAvYrzRQcIe%2F4zZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=11f84876\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mgTq1gYCsZA</a>"},{"pid":"4031eb93248a2dbf7c78a26adbf7d387caf647d1","tid":982922,"uid":78029,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T13:38:53.000Z","msg":"補充: <br />\n1.吸收咗上次教訓, 今次盡量唔CHOK聲, 希望大家聽得舒服少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82a03f9095aa48bbaf529dca7c2bb6c998ce40e1","tid":982922,"uid":78029,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T13:40:06.000Z","msg":"2. 參考咗巴打意見, 