似bug，個t尾入聲讀得唔準<br />\n<br />\n加油呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T16:25:55.000Z","msg":"個「我」字, 我都特登用脷頂上排牙, 估唔到都無NG音, 睇嚟要再練<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n「進」字EON變左UNG, 呢個啱啱知咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n「健」可能合埋咗個口先讀錯? 我知應該唔合<br />\n「干」同「肛」我真係分唔到, 唔係同音字?<br />\n「不」t尾入聲讀得唔準, 我都係講先知有t尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n多謝指正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d8f14eb593e8faeeabb5f1868dd3c462ba6d71c","tid":982922,"uid":77642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"02c170a1b8f753aed6e69e40f2eb94fa350ea017","tid":982922,"uid":78029,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"1a40d710272dc44432474f02363fc1bb45c966d2","tid":982922,"uid":77642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T16:15:45.000Z","msg":"可以留意下以下既字<br />\n<br />\n「我」字 好似讀到無乜NG音<br />\n「進」度 讀到有D似中度<br />\n「健」康 讀到有D似斂康<br />\n「干」擾 讀到有D似肛擾<br />\n「不」似預期 讀到有D似bug，個t尾入聲讀得唔準<br />\n<br />\n加油呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T16:25:55.000Z","msg":"個「我」字, 我都特登用脷頂上排牙, 估唔到都無NG音, 睇嚟要再練<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n「進」字EON變左UNG, 呢個啱啱知咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n「健」可能合埋咗個口先讀錯? 我知應該唔合<br />\n「干」同「肛」我真係分唔到, 唔係同音字?<br />\n「不」t尾入聲讀得唔準, 我都係講先知有t尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n多謝指正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T02:10:29.000Z","msg":"【ng】發音時舌跟頂住上顎後部，讓氣流從鼻腔呼出。<br />\n所以用脷頂上排牙應該出唔到ng音<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n另外可以用中文既粵語配音審詞字庫去check發音<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://humanum.arts.cuhk.edu.hk/Lexis/lexi-can/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhumanum.arts.cuhk.edu.hk%2FLexis%2Flexi-can%2F&d=tZkk7dfkwHAvYrzRQcIe%2F4zZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=70ab2119\" target=\"_blank\">https://humanum.arts.cuhk.edu.hk/Lexis/lexi-can/</a><br />\n干係gon1 肛係gong1，肛係ng尾，所以有喉嚨音，干就無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n「不」個t係粵音既t，唔係英文既t<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可能我講到一舊舊，sorry<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不係bat1，同「乞」個尾一樣，你個發音會似似地「北」，<br />\n即係bak1。<br />\n可以比較下下面既字：<br />\n「策」：-k<br />\n「擦」：-t<br />\n<br />\n「特」：-k<br />\n「突」：-t<br />\n<br />\n「黑」：-k<br />\n「乞」：-t<br />\n<br />\n「墨」：-k<br />\n「勿」：-t<br />\n加油呀，好支持你既片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e117a884311a1f834cd67256f7fa76cb9729ed17","tid":982922,"uid":42762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T07:09:15.000Z","msg":"正呀喂，支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/a